item.description: Join us for Stump Team Trivia at Firefly's in Framingham. Trivia starts at 7:30pm. We will meet at 7pm to get a spot. Join us for drinks, food and a fun time playing team trivia. Everyone is responsible for their own food/drink. Please look for Catherine, if you have trouble finding us please call 774 232 0000.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Stump Team Trivia at Firefly's Framingham
